465
00:35:34,220 --> 00:35:36,160
 A, ide nagrada nakon toga.

466
00:35:36,160 --> 00:35:37,200
 A ili je to...

467
00:35:37,200 --> 00:35:38,200
 Kakav je to pristup?

468
00:35:38,200 --> 00:35:39,680
 Što kažeš o tom pristupu?

469
